  "texts": [
    "In this study, we introduce the Pragmatic Understanding Benchmark (PUB) designed to assess pragmatic comprehension in LLMs.",
    "We offer a comprehensive analysis, providing insights into various aspects of pragmatic understanding within LLMs.",
    "Our findings reveal that pragmatic understanding in LLMs can be enhanced through instruction-tuning of these models.",
    "Interestingly, even without specific fine-tuning, language models at scale exhibit equivalent pragmatic understanding.",
    "Notably, smaller models, particularly the instruction-tuned variants, outperform their base counterparts, but this advantage diminishes as models scale up, with base and instructiontuned models showing comparable performance."
  ],
